•Several of our key raw materials components, particularly CdTe, and manufacturing equipment are either single-sourced
or sourced from a limited number of suppliers, and their failure to perform could cause manufacturing delays and impair
our ability to deliver solar modules to customers in the required quality and quantities and at a price that is profitable to us.
•Our failure to reduce module manufacturing production and selling costs, including costs related to raw materials and
