Unrestricted Stock
During the years ended December 31, 2021, 2020, and 2019, we awarded 19,513; 27,731; and 26,254, respectively, of fully vested,
unrestricted shares of our common stock, excluding amounts withheld for taxes, to the chairman and independent members of our
board of directors. Accordingly, we recognized $1.8 million, $1.5 million, and $1.5 million of share-based compensation expense
for these awards during the years ended December 31, 2021, 2020, and 2019, respectively.
